OL,3,CPolice issue dispersal orders in
OL,4,CCarlisle ahead of potential planned
OL,5,Cdisorder
OL,7,FA dispersal order has been introduced
OL,8,Fby Cumbria Constabulary amid reports
OL,9,Fof potential planned disorder.
OL,11,FAn increased police presence will be
OL,12,Fin place throughout the day in
OL,13,FCarlisle and surrounding areas until
OL,14,Fmidnight 7 August 2024.
OL,16,FLegislation enables officers to carry
OL,17,Fout more stop and searches with the
OL,18,Fauthority to order the removal of face
OL,19,Fcoverings intended to disguise or
OL,20,Fconceal a person's appearance.
