OL,7,FCumbria Police will also be able to
OL,8,Fconfiscate any items used to create
OL,9,Fanti-social behaviour.
OL,11,FChief Superintendent Carl Patrick
OL,12,Fsaid: "The dispersal order and the
OL,13,Fpowers which have been authorised are
OL,14,Fin place to protect our communities
OL,15,Ffrom those who may engage in violent
OL,16,Fdisorder.
OL,18,F"We support and facilitate the right
OL,19,Fto peaceful protest however violent
OL,20,Fdisorder will not be tolerated.
